### **4. main_LiveChartField**  
**Description:**  
Visualizes streaming numerical data on a clean, real-time chart with refresh control.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LiveChartField - Real-Time Stream Graph

LiveChartField transforms metric streams into scrollable, responsive charts ideal for simulations or dashboards.

## Features
- Live updating line chart  
- Adjustable scroll window  
- Matplotlib-powered  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/main_LiveChartField.git
cd main_LiveChartField
python visualize.py
